763
01:32:52,600 --> 01:32:54,100
"Hocu, majko."

764
01:32:57,600 --> 01:32:59,600
"Bila sam dobra majka, zar ne?"

765
01:33:01,000 --> 01:33:02,200
"Jesi, majko."

766
01:33:10,400 --> 01:33:12,600
Sacuvati njen poslednji dah!

767
01:33:17,700 --> 01:33:19,500
"Volim te, Guy!"

768
01:33:21,800 --> 01:33:23,400
"I ja ..."

769
01:34:15,500 --> 01:34:17,400
Guy...
beznadezno sam!

770
01:34:47,000 --> 01:34:48,800
A sad treci premaz...

771
